=== Transitive verb ===
'''to read''' /ri:d/ [[imp.]] & [[p.p.]] also spelled ''read'' but pronounced /rεd/

#look at and interpret letters or other information that is [[written]]
#speak from a written book
#is interpreted (''Arabic reads backwards'')
#hear (especially in CB parlance) ''Do you read me?'' [CB = Citizens' Band (US unlicensed amateur radio)]
#to make a special study of, as by perusing textbooks; as, to read theology or law.

